body:
Bisected this to [#11245](https://github.com/bevyengine/bevy/pull/11245)
Specifically, the deletion of these lines
```
        if runner_state.redraw_requested {
            let (_, winit_windows, _, _) = event_writer_system_state.get_mut(&mut app.world);
            for window in winit_windows.windows.values() {
                window.request_redraw();
            }
        }
```
adding these lines back fixes the bug, but I'm not sure if that would regress the original pull or introduce other issues
